      "author": "dipro (Dipro Bhowmik)",
      "cookedHtml": "<h3><a name=\"p-33535-yep-you-heard-us-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-33535-yep-you-heard-us-1\"></a>Yep, you heard us!</h3>\n<p>We just released 8 React components that you can use in your monday apps!</p>\n<p>Now you can make your custom app look like monday, without having to rebuild all the UI elements from scratch.</p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-33535-can-i-contribute-my-own-components-2\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-33535-can-i-contribute-my-own-components-2\"></a>Can I contribute my own components?</h3>\n<p>You sure can! Read our <a href=\"https://github.com/mondaycom/monday-ui-react-core/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md\">Contributing Guidelines</a> to learn how you can add your own components to the monday library.</p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-33535-whats-next-3\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-33535-whats-next-3\"></a>What’s next?</h3>\n<p>We’re going to release more components later in the year. Which ones would you like to see?</p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-33535-how-do-i-access-them-4\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-33535-how-do-i-access-them-4\"></a>How do I access them?</h3>\n<p>Head to this Github repo to learn more: <a href=\"https://github.com/mondaycom/monday-ui-react-core\">monday UI React Core</a></p>\n<p>You can also access them directly from our <a href=\"https://monday.com/developers/apps/intro\">apps documentation</a>: </p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/8/8e6574738aec02cf82da2050fb2b689f0df01226.png\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/8/8e6574738aec02cf82da2050fb2b689f0df01226_2_345x180.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"345\" height=\"180\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">2756×1442 420 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-33535-included-components-5\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-33535-included-components-5\"></a>Included components:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://style.monday.com/?path=/story/components-button--default-story\">Button</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://style.monday.com/?path=/story/components-icon--icons\">Icon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://style.monday.com/?path=/story/components-text-field--sandbox\">Text field</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://style.monday.com/?path=/story/components-search--sandbox\">Search box</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://style.monday.com/?path=/story/components-loader--sizes\">Loader</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://style.monday.com/?path=/story/components-tooltip--sandbox\">Tooltip</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://style.monday.com/?path=/story/components-link--sandbox\">Link</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://style.monday.com/?path=/story/components-linearprogressbar--sandbox\">Linear progress bar</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Heads up, <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/kaminskypavel\">@kaminskypavel</a> <a class=\"mention-group\" href=\"/groups/community-experts\">@community-experts</a> <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/blush.png?v=15\" title=\":blush:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":blush:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>"
